           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "K"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      70                   to   v-pos                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                                      *-------------------------*
